cast.overview: It’s the summer before Elle heads to college, and she has a secret decision to make. Elle has been accepted into Harvard, where boyfriend Noah is matriculating, and also Berkeley, where her BFF Lee is headed and has to decide if she should stay or not.
cast.title: The Kissing Booth 3

details.biography: Daneel van der Walt is a South African, bilingual actress and singer. She played the beloved character of Suzette in Nêrens Noord-Kaap, Anna in Recipes for Love and Murder and Bianca in Fraksie. She has appeared in several local South African soap operas and telenovelas including Suidooster and Arendsvlei.  She is also a talented singer and cabaret artist who writes her own songs. She won a Fleur Du Cap award for her portrayal of Magenta in the Rocky Horror Show.
details.name: Daneel Van Der Walt
